WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.269 --> 00:00:10.200
In the ancient lands of feudal Japan,

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:14.250
dwelled a mysterious and evil clan of Black
Ninja Stress Balls,

00:00:14.250 --> 00:00:17.050
known only as "The Shadow Clan."

00:00:17.970 --> 00:00:22.520
High in their mountain fortress they train
night and day, perfecting the soft and squishy

00:00:22.520 --> 00:00:23.740
art of combat.

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:24.789
"Again!"

00:00:25.879 --> 00:00:30.110
The Black Shadow Clan is well known for their
ruthless nature and are the cause of great

00:00:30.110 --> 00:00:32.130
stress to the villagers in the town below.

00:00:32.340 --> 00:00:35.640
"Soon we will show the villagers who is in
control of these lands."

00:00:35.640 --> 00:00:37.180
(Applause, cheers)

00:00:37.340 --> 00:00:38.590
"Aaaaah!"

00:00:41.860 --> 00:00:44.080
"It's the Blue Ninja Stress Ball! Get him!"

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:52.240
(Awesome Fight Music Plays)

00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:52.940
"You!"

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.140
"You bring great dishonor to your family and
all stress balls."

00:00:56.149 --> 00:00:58.440
"Honor is meant for those with power."

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:02.380
"A Stress Ball Ninja's true honor comes through
service to others.

00:01:02.380 --> 00:01:06.000
We are meant to relieve stress and bring tranquility
to those around us.

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:10.700
You create only strife. I wander the land,
using my gifts and training to promote any

00:01:10.860 --> 00:01:12.630
company or team that needs my services.

00:01:12.630 --> 00:01:16.010
For this is the true path of a slayer of stress."

00:01:16.220 --> 00:01:17.500
"I will slay you!"

00:01:17.740 --> 00:01:22.580
(Awesome Fight Music Again)

00:01:22.700 --> 00:01:26.100
(Person Making Fighting Noises)

00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:28.160
"You are defeated."

00:01:28.170 --> 00:01:33.090
"Promoting other's brands for the guaranteed
lowest price has made you strong.

00:01:33.619 --> 00:01:35.369
Teach us your ways, Master."

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:42.800
"I will. And together we will bring peace
and harmony back to this land."

